Interface ManagementDelegate

  • All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface ManagementDelegate
extends Management

    Title: ManagementDelegate.java

    Description: An extension of the management subsystem interface that can be wrapped by a Journal module. At some point it may contain methods, but for now it is just a tagging interface.
